  "title": "Property Executive | Commercial Building | Senior / Junior | Central Area",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a leading Real Estate company. They are looking for a Senior/Building Executive to assist their Building team for the next phrase of their business. They are located at Central of Singapore– easily accessible. The Senior/Building Executive is responsible for:</strong></p><p><strong>Duties</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Building Inspections & Maintenance</strong>: Conduct daily inspections, address issues, and recommend improvements to ensure optimal building conditions.</li><li><strong>Facilities & Contractor Management</strong>: Oversee security, cleaning, landscaping, waste management, and building systems while ensuring contractors meet service standards.</li><li><strong>Fire & Safety Compliance</strong>: Act as a CERT member, conduct fire system inspections, and execute fire drills.</li><li><strong>Stakeholder & Tenant Engagement</strong>: Maintain strong tenant relationships, handle feedback, and coordinate improvement works with relevant authorities.</li><li><strong>Budget & Procurement Oversight</strong>: Assist in budgeting, manage contracts, and ensure proper record-keeping for building operations.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Building Management & Services, or equivalent</li><li>Good-grade business commercial building experience</li><li>Experience in building soft services facilities management</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p>Email Address: <strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9682</p><p>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
